	drivedb.h:
	- Samsung based SSDs: SM843TN *960HCGP (#1624), PM881
	  (GH/pull 119), more PM893 variants (#1616), PM897 (#1559).
	- USB: Genesys Logic: Merge entries, add 0x05e3:0x2013.
	- USB: ADATA SD600 (0x125f:0xa68a).

