2019-10-19  Christian Franke  <franke@computer.org>

	scsiprint.cpp: Silence 'value never read' warning from clang
	analyzer.

	Avoid usage of asctime(), ctime(), gmtime(), and localtime().
	Use thread-safe *_r() or *_s() variants instead.
